# ── .NET build output (in submodule + anywhere else) ──────────────────────
**/bin/
**/obj/

# ── Frontend ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/
Maia.Client/dist/
Maia.Client/.angular/

# ── IDE / tooling ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
.claude/
*.user
*.suo

# ── OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# ── MS Office temp/lock files (e.g. ~$ToDo.docx) ─────────────────────────
~$*

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log

# ── Server secrets: the deployed connection strings / credentials live only on
#    the server, never in the repo. The checked-in appsettings.json holds dev
#    placeholders; Production is provisioned per-host. ───────────────────────
Maia.Services/Maia.API/appsettings.Production.json
appsettings.*.Local.json

# ── .NET publish output (build artifacts — regenerable, never commit) ──────
Maia.Services/Maia.API/publish/
Maia.Services/Maia.API/publish-fx/
